177 A.3d 122 STATE OF NEW JERSEY, PLAINTIFF-RESPONDENT, v. ENZO R. PENA, DEFENDANT-PETITIONER.

C-442 September Term 2017

079697 December 18, 2017

ON PETITION FOR CERTIFICATION

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-000350-15 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
